<div class="image_bg">
	<div class="image_left">
         	<img src="/images/gift.gif" height="200px" width="250px" /> 
        </div>
	<div class="image_right">
		<p><span>LittleSurprizes</span> lets you send surprise gifts to your friends on facebook on their special days like birthday and anniversary.</p>
		<p>You can contribute to your friend's wishlist by simply shopping for yourself through our website 
<a href="#">www.littlesurprizes.com </a></p>
	
		<p>Remember, you don't have to purchase a gift, just shop for yourself via our site.</p>	
	</div>	
</div>

<%if @wish_list.nil? and current_user and !admin?%>
  	<p class="text">No Items Found In Your Wish List.</p>
<%end%>

<div class="sidebar">
    	<h2>Category list</h2>
	<ul id='tree'><%= render :partial => 'category_list', :collection => @parent, :as => :category %></ul>

<% @banners.each do |banner| %>
    <%=h banner.name %><br/>
    <%= link_to image_tag(banner.banner_image.url(:thumb)),banner.url,:target=>'_blank'%><br/>
<% end %>


</div>

<div class="container">
	<h2>LittleSurprizes will do the rest.</h2>
	<p> Based on your shopping, we will send your friend a surprise gift in the names of the friends, like you, who contributed to the gift. </p>
	<p>You can also do monetary contributions to your friends wishlist. You can create a wishlist and start contributing for your own littlesurprizes gift too!
Try it out! It is absolutely FREE!!!</p>
	
	<div id = 'category-list'>
   		<%= render :partial => 'list' %>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>


